  }, "v33"), mdx("p", null, "CH\xDAA To\xE0n N\u0103ng ph\xE1n nh\u01B0 sau: \"D\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en v\xE0 Giu-\u0111a l\xE0 t\xF4i m\u1ECDi. K\u1EBB th\xF9 b\u1EAFt ch\xFAng l\xE0m t\xF9 binh, kh\xF4ng ch\u1ECBu th\u1EA3 ra. "), mdx("h6", {
