  }, "v34"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u01B0ng Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF r\u1EA5t m\u1EA1nh n\xEAn s\u1EBD chu\u1ED9c ch\xFAng l\u1EA1i. Danh Ng\xE0i l\xE0 CH\xDAA To\xE0n N\u0103ng. Ng\xE0i ch\u1EAFc ch\u1EAFn s\u1EBD d\xF9ng quy\u1EC1n n\u0103ng m\xECnh b\u1EA3o v\u1EC7 ch\xFAng, \u0111\u1EC3 ban cho x\u1EE9 s\u1EF1 an ngh\u1EC9. Nh\u01B0ng Ng\xE0i s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng ban s\u1EF1 y\xEAn ngh\u1EC9 cho nh\u1EEFng k\u1EBB s\u1ED1ng trong Ba-by-l\xF4n.\" "), mdx("h6", {
