  }, "v36"), mdx("p", null, "H\xE3y cho g\u01B0\u01A1m gi\u1EBFt c\xE1c ti\xEAn tri gi\u1EA3 c\u1EE7a n\xF3, \u0111\u1EC3 ch\xFAng tr\u1EDF n\xEAn ngu d\u1EA1i. H\xE3y \u0111\u1EC3 g\u01B0\u01A1m gi\u1EBFt c\xE1c chi\u1EBFn s\u0129 n\xF3, th\xEC ch\xFAng s\u1EBD kinh ho\xE0ng. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v37"
  }, "v37"), mdx("p", null, "H\xE3y \u0111\u1EC3 g\u01B0\u01A1m gi\u1EBFt ng\u1EF1a v\xE0 qu\xE2n xa c\xF9ng c\xE1c l\xEDnh \u0111\xE1nh thu\xEA t\u1EEB c\xE1c n\u01B0\u1EDBc kh\xE1c. R\u1ED3i ch\xFAng s\u1EBD kinh khi\u1EBFp nh\u01B0 \u0111\xE0n b\xE0. H\xE3y \u0111\u1EC3 g\u01B0\u01A1m t\u1EA5n c\xF4ng c\xE1c kho t\xE0ng n\xF3, \u0111\u1EC3 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ta c\u01B0\u1EDBp ch\xFAng \u0111i. "), mdx("h6", {
