    "id": "v45"
  }, "v45"), mdx("p", null, "Cho n\xEAn h\xE3y nghe \u0111i\u1EC1u CH\xDAA d\u1EF1 \u0111\u1ECBnh l\xE0m ngh\u1ECBch l\u1EA1i Ba-by-l\xF4n. H\xE3y nghe \u0111i\u1EC1u Ng\xE0i \u0111\xE3 quy\u1EBFt \u0111\u1ECBnh l\xE0m cho d\xE2n th\xE0nh Ba-by-l\xF4n. Ng\xE0i ch\u1EAFc ch\u1EAFn s\u1EBD l\xF4i c\xE1c trai tr\xE1ng c\u1EE7a Ba-by-l\xF4n \u0111i. Qu\xEA qu\xE1n ch\xFAng n\xF3 s\u1EBD kinh ho\xE0ng khi nh\xECn th\u1EA5y s\u1ED1 ph\u1EADn ch\xFAng n\xF3. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v46"
  }, "v46"), mdx("p", null, "Khi nghe Ba-by-l\xF4n b\u1ECB chi\u1EBFm, \u0111\u1EA5t s\u1EBD rung chuy\u1EC3n. D\xE2n ch\xFAng c\xE1c n\u01B0\u1EDBc s\u1EBD nghe ti\u1EBFng k\xEAu tuy\u1EC7t v\u1ECDng c\u1EE7a Ba-by-l\xF4n."), mdx("hr", null), mdx("p", null, "", mdx("a", {
